# CODEOWNERS — review automático em PRs
# Sintaxe: <pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default — owner do repo aprova tudo
* @euvhmac

# Documentação arquitetural — owner deve revisar
/docs/                 @euvhmac
/docs/adr/             @euvhmac

# Infrastructure — high-impact + custo
/infra/                @euvhmac
/.github/              @euvhmac
/.github/workflows/    @euvhmac

# Foundation files
/.github/copilot-instructions.md  @euvhmac
/.github/instructions/            @euvhmac

# Security-sensitive
/lambda/               @euvhmac
**/secrets/            @euvhmac
**/.env.example        @euvhmac

# Data contracts
**/schema.yml          @euvhmac
**/sources.yml         @euvhmac
